title: Black Sabbath fans queue up to watch the band's last ever gig | Central
text:
Black Sabbath fans were seen queuing up outside the Birmingham Genting Arena, ahead of the band's last ever concert .
Credit: ITV Central/ Lee Comley Rock star Ozzy Osbourne said earlier, he is emotional as his heavy metal band Black Sabbath prepare for their last ever shows this weekend.
The group, which is credited with creating heavy metal, is drawing the final curtain on their generation-crossing career with two shows in their home city of Birmingham.
Credit: ITV Central/ Lee Comley Black Sabbath Ozzy Osbourne Birmingham West Midlands
